i never ever write in this thing anymore..i used to be obsessed no lie..so i guess some ppl hate me..and other are mad at me..and to tell u the truth..i dont really care anymore..cause its all pointless shit..if ur mad at me..tell me..dont go telling other ppl.."omg i cant believe her..."..dude i dont wanna deal with ppl like that..i dont need that right now..id rather u say it to my face..just walk right up to me and say "yo bitch, i fucking hate you"..cause in all honesty its a lot easy for me to hear it from u then to hear it from other ppl who dont even know y..and u kno whats worse..those ppl who totally ignore u when they're mad at u..cause then u dont even kno y they are..cause they wont talk to u..i think its wicked funny ur like omg y did i lose all my old friends..the thing is u left them..u got new friends first..u moved on..they never left u behind..

Because once upon a time, we were best friends. And, yes, there's been a lot of bad stuff in between. But none of that matters right now, okay? You need me, I'm there. Any time, any place, anywhere

Maybe some friendships aren't meant to be saved. Maybe we're meant to spend a certain part of our life with certain people...and then move on

Breaking up with your boyfriend is a million times easier than breaking up with your best friend

wicked bored..and alone on a fri night..woohoo..i got the house to myself..and i dont kno when ppl are coming home..i kinda dont like being home alone though..its too quiet esp  for my house..the radios blasting..just to get some noise..kinda makes me feel like a loser..yeah..nothing new really..yeah theres ur update..

wow kids..i havent been on my journal in forever!..goodness..well last night i hit up the Big E..fun for sure..*innocent smile*..im such a rebel..lets see lets see..16 still w/o my permit..idk ive been pretty busy..i kno no excuse for not getting it..schools been pretty gay..but its to be expected..latin..o man..worst class like ever..but u kno whatever..so gym tennis is over..heartbreaking really..anyways..my new comp should be in tomorrow..woohoo.. pumped for that..omg..my preschooler is the absolute cutest sweetest little kid ever..i cant wait til they all come to school..but we still have to do soo much before they come..school tomorrow..def dont want to go..but then again i do..football game fri..home game..come visit me and the rest of the wicked cool band kids..soccer game today..kinda dont wanna go..but im "needed"..umm what else..yay..me and jgann are gonna hang today!!!...omg i havent chilled with that girl in forever..wicked pumped..lalalala..sry..randomly busting out singin..o man..cant wait for the band to hit up the big e the 29th..itll be fun..cant wait..well i gotta do something..like now..cause im in a wicked good mood..2 reasons..ill tell u kids later..

back to school..and finally 16..yet without a permit..fucking gay..lets see..school hasnt been too bad..i like my classes for the most part..and i got preschool..wicked pumped..the only bad thing i like never see ANYONE..thats kinda ok..cause we can all chill on the weekends..so..mon was my birthday..wanted to get my permit..didnt happen..wayyy too busy..tues..wanted to get my permit.mom and dad waayyy to busy (even though i didnt do anything yesterday)..today..wanted to get my permit..went to the mall to get clothes instead..cause mom didnt want to drive me to springfield..im starting to think they dont want me to get my permit..what is this..ahh..i might go crazy if i dont get it soon..thats about it..later days

omg today was a blast..well it started off not soo cool..with running around cleaning and work..ha sry i left u kels..but the dentist chair was calling..woohoo..went to the dentist fun fun..wisdom teeth r to come out soon..woohoo..then came the party..omg it was a blast..thanks for al the gifts guys..i thought it was wicked nice that keith called from florida to say happy birthday..i hope u all had as much fun as i did..i cant believe school starts mon..omg im wicked pumped..too bad i dont kno my fricken schedual..messed up school..leave it to westfield..

where to start..hmm..working a ton..yesterday i worked..fun stuff..then after work i went to 6 flags with julia..o good god..teacups~not kool~i finally got my pics developed! woohoo..pumped..school starts in 5 days..and omg..i turen 16 in 5 days..kinda excited for school..social aspect of course..dude i want my schedual like really bad..the frosh got theirs..and some of my friends got theirs..and last year we got them the last day of school..whats with the change?..band camp thing tonight..woohoo..katie has my flute and shes in maine..so im gonna tell mr k its in the shop..whoops..im thinking thats about it for now..maybe..

lets see lets see..i turn 16 in 8 days..we go back to school in 8 days.. fun fun..im actually kinda excited to go back..i kno, i must be crazy..but im getting bored of summer..i wanna see ppl from school..not everyone for sure..but my friends and ppl i havent seen all summer..i want my schedual so i can go down and fix it..cause we all kno they messed something up..come on now..its westfield..well i had some ppl over thurs..that was fun..woohoo..bonfire..keith yet again didnt come..and when we called to see if he was coming..he said he would call later..big suprise~he didnt..got in a fight with my parents..w/e..i dont really care..yesterday i worked at the westfield fair for julias mom..ad i watched the miss westfield fair thing..interesting..has anyone noticed that pagent moms/dads are really ugly..or is it just me..well nothing else new really..
aww..read the paper yesterday..obituaries that is..a kid our age from our school in my class died..matthew dandurand..wicked sad..i didnt kno him and i dont kno how he died..but rest in peace matt..

Oh my fricken god~ i just got back from camp..and holy shit it was fricken awesome..i would tell u all everything but 1 u wouldnt understand and 2 theres wayyy tooo much to write about..all in all i had so much fun..is crazy..the first couple days ur like counting down when u get to leave and then the last days ur like omg we're leaving soon..i've been home a little over an hour and i already miss ppl from camp..im pumped to be home though, i miss u guys a ton im kinda tired right now..cause i stayed up all night..talking to one of the kids i met..we chased racoons out of the site the whole night while everyone else slept..it was pretty crazy..idk what else to write..cause everything i could write about no one would understand cause u weren't there and u dont kno the ppl that were..

well last night was a blast..me and the girls (lora, julia, kate, and kels) went to see charlie and the chocolate factory..ha we all said the same thing in the end..we should have been high to see that movie..but it was a ton of fun..i leave for camp today..ill be gone for a whole week..and i cant bring my cell..so dont bother trying to call/text me..cause ur efforts will be useless..but other then the no cell no comp thing im kinda pumped..i love camping..i love being outdoors..woot woot..well i gues thats about it..

well today i worked.. fun fun..allen was gonna give me guitar lessons..but opps..i forgot my guitar..but i promised i would bring it..and i have to play tennis next time..lovely..well work was a blast me and nikki b were crazy and soo bored..i think we goofed off more than we worked..im planning a movie night for tomorrow..im not sure if its gonna happen..but i wanna see everyone before i go to camp..ggrr..a week w/e my cell..i might just die..umm nothing else really..

lets see what have i been up to..hmm..working, hanging with julia, working more, being grounded..i think that about sums what ive done..but in detail..here we go.. last night julia slept over..we did koolaid shots..o  man..i felt soo sick..eeww..lets not do that again..umm lora came and chilled for a while..i made chocolate cake..omg it was good..mm i live cake..ha its amazing im not huge..25 days am ill be 16..woot woot..god im pumped..25 days and school starts..not as pumped..but still exciting..finished my summer reading book in 2 days..it was pretty good..nothing else really..o wait im gonna have a guitar lesson on fri..with a kid at the club..exciting..idk..i have to play tennis soon..i might die..o man..summer camp next week..i cant have my phone..so im going a whole week w/o a phone, comp, radio, cds..i might just die..eww and we have to go swimming..one piece..lovely..so next week dont try and get in contact with me..unless u wanna call my phone and leave a message..

got back from the cape an hour or so ago..o man it was fun..but im in soo much pain..dude sunburn..being so white doesnt help much..now im all red..it kills..umm it was cool cause we went with my cousin  his dad and his dads gf..it was a blast..i may have him shadow me when school comes back around..itd be interesting..thats for sure..im glad to be home..but aug 7 i think..that week im gone for camp..god..i live out of my backpack..aahhh..aleo vera..

got back from boston last night..o man it was a ton of fun..i cant wait to go to college(seein as though im planning to go in boston)..me and kels decide we're gonna move there..camping was horrible..o man..so many bugs.. and other girls that were with us never stoped talking they kept everyone up til all hours of the night..so im wicked tired..umm i leave for the cape today..god im always on the go..i wont be back til wed or thurs..i dont even kno..i need a vacation from my vacations..i just want my own bed and my music blasting..

well lets see where to start..ive been in maine since sat...loads of fun..ha ha not..old ppl are soooooo boring..all they talk about are more old ppl...umm dont really wanna write much about that..umm today i came home..went to the park to play some tennis with gihon, julia w, jess h, and erica..it was a ton of fun..tomorrow morning i leave for boston..then sun i leave for the cape til thurs..so tonight is like the one night i get to sleep in my own bed..and right now it sounds like a plan..

well katie slept over last night..we worked at the club..fun fun..on the way home we got a flat..5 houses away from my house the tired comes off the rim..o yeah..it was down pouring..so me and katie ran home in the rain..ha way too much fun..went to the park today with katie and keith..fun fun..i got soaked..thanks a ton..yeah keith drenched us with his nalgene..then he killed a butterfly..we played some pretty intense frisbee..it was fun..i leave for maine tonight.. wont be back til wed..woot woot..well thats about it

tennis today was a blast jess..wayyy too much fundude it was soo phat..or sciknee..haha..o man watch out for those butterflies..i cant wait til next week..gihons house..o man..im pumped..yeah me and jess h hit up the park and played some intense tennis..it was great..umm i worked this morning..what fun..nothing else..katie is gonna sleep over again tomorrow..cant wait..then sat we're going to the park with keith..should be fun..nothing else really..

well katie slept over last night..it was soo much fun..we played THE CARD GAME..like a million times..there were some interesting results..we called keith and we played THE CARD GAME with him..and it was interesting as well..fun stuff..i cant wait til later..cmp dance off..and then kgrants party..tomorrow im playing tennis..fri katie might sleepover again..sat im going to the park with katie and keith..and then im going to another party..then its off to maine til wed..im kinda pumped..but its been pretty crazy..

well yesterday i was completely bored..so i sat around my house..til it was time for work..lovely..it wasnt as bad as usual, but it was me, kels, jessie, nikki, and hailey, so we were all working pretty hard..poor hailey couldnt carry the trays..but other than that everything went pretty smooth..i got yet again no sleep..last night or the night before..but i've lost so much sleep i dont feel tired anymore..i dont think im doing anything today..maybe ill hit up the park..idk..

well last night went to fiores party last night..it was pretty fun..me and lora chilled out most of the night..cause everyone was playing truth or dare..and we didnt really want to play..it was interesting..me lora and keith ha d a nice convo about carrots..goodness..it was pretty fun..some interesting things happened..got me gihon and lora thinking..well thats about it for now i guess..

well yesterday i went to my uncles house for the big 4th of july party thing..it was kinda fun..me and tony chilled inside while all the kids ran around the house..when we were little me and him were almost like siblings..and i havent seen him in forever..so it was really kool..even if he does like the yankees..and we had to watch the yankees game~which they won~woot i guess..umm work was intense..we had jr golf and regular lunch so i was going crazy working 2 rooms..i was gonna play tennis..but i didnt want to..idk..im wicked tired..and i put my stuff in my tent cause god knows i wont be able to sleep in my house...ppl are so damn loud..OMG! fricken bug bites..bug spray sucks ass..

well last night at the fireworks saw a ton of ppl..some i wanted to see others i didnt..but it was still fun..poor julia w, she missed out this year cause shes in murtle beach..but im sure they have pretty kool fireworks down there..amanda looks like a fricken mexican, shes soo dark..goodness..umm watching the traffic from my house wasnt too bad..it was flowing pretty well..haha..when jess w and her family left i had to direct traffic to help them get out of the driveway..it was pretty funny..i thought i was gonna get ht by a car..sarah d slept over..in the tent in the backyard..omg it was cold..a lot of fun..i have to make cheesecake for my uncles party today..fun fun..hope my cousins there..i havent seen him in forever..well thats about it..
well it seems like a nice day for some fireworks..omg cant wait..im still really tired..i tried to sleep in..ha that didnt work..umm nothing really to talk about..except how stupid i feel..but yeah..
